<li><span>The primary language of delivery for this program is English.&nbsp;</span></li>
<li><span>There are two accessible parking spaces located in the front parking lot on Rowley Avenue. Each space is roughly 20 m from the front entrance (accessible via ramp) also located on Rowley Avenue. Additional parking is located behind the building on David Drive.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>
<li><span>The nearest <a href="https://plan.octranspo.com/plan">bus stops</a> are located at Meadowlands/Peter, Meadowlands/Perry, and Meadowlands/Savuto, approximately 300 m from the museum.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>
